page.title: 10Queensbury Teacher
page.content: A Rhodesway school teacher. Most people would have there famly living in Queensbury. I was brought up in Queensbury and friends from about 2 years old still live in Queensbury. When I want to entertain my/self I take the dog for a walk or do abit of gardening like I say Queensbury is almost Isloted. There are a few nice pubs in Queensbury. There is almost no polution in Queensbury because its all farming land and grass land. As in Bradford there's all the factories and mills working all day. There's some factories in Queensbury but only a few.
